                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 367.114M69/141.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Consul General at
                            Smyrna</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate General</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Smyrna</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-06-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 26, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Captain of the <hi rend="italic">Texas</hi> has been removed from the
                    hospital prison and thrown into the common prison of condemned criminals.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Horton</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
